Django Web Framework Implementation:
Models:

    BursaryApplication:
        Fields:
            National ID Number (CharField)
            Student Registration Number (CharField)
            Institution Name (ForeignKey to Institution model)
            Institution Account Number (CharField)
            Financial Year (CharField)
            Serial Number (CharField)
            Date Submitted (DateTimeField)
            Amount Disbursed (DecimalField)
            Date Disbursed (DateTimeField)

    Institution:
        Fields:
            Name (CharField)

Templates:

    landing_page.html:
        Display landing page with the current bursary application status.
        Show "Apply" and "Track Progress" buttons.

    application_form.html:
        Display Tertiary Institution type dropdown.
        Form for entering personal details (National ID, Student Registration Number, Institution details).

    success_page.html:
        Display success message with the decrypted serial number.
        Provide options to save the serial number as PNG or PDF.

    progress_report.html:
        Display the generated report with student details, amount disbursed, and date disbursed.
        Provide an option to save the report as a PDF.

Forms:

    ApplicationForm:
        Fields:
            National ID Number
            Student Registration Number
            Institution Name
            Institution Account Number
        Validation:
            Check validity of National ID and Student Registration Number.
            Verify eligibility and registration in Kisumu West Constituency.
            Validate against the current students register of the chosen institution for the given academic year.

    ProgressTrackingForm:
        Fields:
            Serial Number

Views:

    LandingPageView:
        Display landing page with the current application status.

    ApplicationFormView:
        Handle GET request: Display the application form.
        Handle POST request: Validate and process form data.

    SuccessPageView:
        Display the success page with the decrypted serial number.

    ProgressReportView:
        Generate and display the progress report for a valid serial number.

URLs:

from django.urls import path
from .views import LandingPageView, ApplicationFormView, SuccessPageView, TrackProgressView, ProgressReportView

urlpatterns = [
    path('', LandingPageView.as_view(), name='landing_page'),
    path('apply/', ApplicationFormView.as_view(), name='apply'),
    path('success/', SuccessPageView.as_view(), name='success'),
    path('progress-report/', ProgressReportView.as_view(), name='progress_report'),
]

UI/UX Recommendations:

    Color Scheme and Styling:
        Use a clean and simple design with a blue and white color scheme.
        Differentiate interactive elements with distinct colors (Blue for primary, Green for positive actions, Red for negative actions).

    Error Handling:
        Provide clear and concise error messages in red for better visibility.
        Ensure validation errors are highlighted and explained.

    Form Design:
        Use intuitive icons for actions like submit, cancel, and clear.
        Ensure a responsive design for a seamless user experience across devices.

    Progress Indicators:
        Include progress indicators (Blue Progress Bar) during lengthy processes to keep users informed.

    User Guidance:
        Use tooltips or info icons for guiding users through complex processes.

    Typography and Spacing:
        Implement a user-friendly font (Arial or Roboto) and ensure proper spacing for readability.

    Navigation:
        Optimize the layout for easy navigation between sections.
        Provide a consistent navigation experience across the application.

